The shopkeeper~
A fat little halfling shopkeeper smiles broadly at you.
~
As the halfling notices your gaze he immediately begins to chatter away
cheerfully, talking about the latest gossip and asking you about your
adventures.  He flips the dragonwings on the grill skillfully and bastes
it with his special barbeque sauce without missing a beat in his
conversation.  He tells you that the "dragonwings" aren't actually made
out of dragons wings, but he couldn't possibly give away the recipe because
it is a trade secret passed down in his family for many generations.  He
truely loves his job and enjoys the company of the "many great heroes",
as he likes to call the members of Honor.
