#31500
The Path to Honor~
As you approach a large iron gate, a weathered old man wanders out of the
guardhouse to greet you.  Before you, a brick path makes its way up a 
hill, lined with trees as old as the city of Midgaard itself and providing
a pleasant shade from the hot summer sun.  You lift your eyes to the end of
the path and see the stone steps leading to the large entrance of the hall
of the clan Honor, its foundations firmly laid upon a fortified hill.  Four
large towers reach upward from the corners of the stone structure.  The
strength eminating from the fortress encourages you, reminding you of the
many legendary men and women of Honor who fought to defend their clan;
the clan you now call your own.
~
