Stymie's Room~
You have walked into a room that appears to be a shrine of punk rock. As
you look around, you see memorabilia from some of the greatest punk
bands known to man. There are autographed billboards and fliers from
bands such as the Sex Pistols, The Ramones, The Misfits, and Generation
X to name just a few. As you walk further into this sanctuary, you hear
a strange sound emanating in the air. You suddenly feel the urge to slam
dance as the sounds take control of your mind.
 
You quickly regain your composure and continue exploring this strange
and unique abode. As you look further into the room, you come across a
ghastly sight. You swear it can't be but there is no mistaking it! You
see this thing in the corner and you scream and run for the door to tell
everyone of the horrors that lies beyond these doors. You are asked what
the most frightening thing you saw was, to which you reply "In the
corner was... was the most horrifying thing I ever saw. It was.... It
was......."
