Nyaxtor's Lair~
You step into a seemingly dank and lifeless cavern.
 
Soft and soulful jazz music eminates from the walls. You hear a voice from
somewhere in the dark back of the cave say "Hey baby, come on back here and
I'll show you a good time,".  Taking this unknown voice up on its offer ,
you step cautiously towards its source.  Suddenly a lava lamp lights up and
spreads its groovy light throughout the cave.  The light reveals what looks
like a really nifty bead curtain.  You part the beads and enter the hidden
room. The floor is carpeted with a very hip shag rug.   Sitting temptingly
on a bean bag chair is a youthful and virile looking silver dragon.  He
extends a claw and pulls you down into his lap, tail thumping happily on the
floor.  "Welcome to the Lair o' Love, baby," he says with a devilish grin...
~
